Open anaconda power shell on your windows machine.
Create virtual environment using the command below:
cd '.\NLP Deploy YT\' #Change directory until you reach the project directory
conda env list #to see the virtual environments existing in you conda
conda create -n zelai python=3.9 #To create a new virtual environment named zelai with python 3.9
pip install --upgrade pip # to upgrade pip if some errors show up with it
pip install flask
Incase of any errors with other libraries use pip install the_lib_name

Other commands
conda remove --name zelai --all #incase you want to delete a virtual environment 
